HEADWORD: Abdominous
<hw>Ab*dom"i*nous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a
protuberant belly; pot-bellied.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Gorgonius sits, <qex>abdominous</qex> and wan,⟦br⟧
